### **RESTful API Design**

**HTTP Method Best Practices:**

```
GET    /api/users          - List all users
GET    /api/users/:id      - Get single user
POST   /api/users          - Create user
PUT    /api/users/:id      - Update user (full)
PATCH  /api/users/:id      - Update user (partial)
